sections.Biography:
===Background===
Aggo was a member of [[Khal]] [[Drogo]]'s [[khalasar]] and a member of Daenerys' ''khas''. When Drogo's khalasar fractures, he remains loyal to Daenerys. He pledges his fealty to her after the birth of the dragons. She names his as one of her [[bloodrider]]s alongside [[Rakharo]] and [[Kovarro]].&lt;ref name=&quot;E11&quot;&gt;&quot;[[The North Remembers]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 2]]===
Daenerys leads what remains of her khalasar deep into the Red Waste. Facing starvation she sends Rakharo, Aggo, and Kovarro to scout in three different directions, using the last remaining horses. Aggo is sent southeast.&lt;ref name=&quot;E11&quot;/&gt;
